    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2>《凌盘之境》是一款回合制战棋游戏，本游戏中采用9*9可转动棋盘设计，将转动的棋盘和地形结合，创造出更具策略性的游戏，转动棋盘是你在战斗中取胜的关键。通过合理转动棋盘，你可以改变地形、移动路径和敌人的位置，以获取最佳战略优势。在游戏中真正体现，牵一发而动全身。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> 独特的棋盘转动机制，将棋盘转动与地形结合。棋盘转动是这个游戏的核心玩法，你可以转动棋盘，解除危机，击杀敌人，营救敌人，获取能量球等操作。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399860/extras/49f62ae1811dfc3d2c4a5a0310830c8d.poster.avif?t=1698402706\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399860/extras/49f62ae1811dfc3d2c4a5a0310830c8d.webm?t=1698402706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399860/extras/49f62ae1811dfc3d2c4a5a0310830c8d.mp4?t=1698402706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> 棋盘转动和地形构造，地形机关相结合，从而创造更多的可能性和策略性。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399860/extras/474063e861fc0994e0d8db59bb8f75e2.poster.avif?t=1698402706\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399860/extras/474063e861fc0994e0d8db59bb8f75e2.webm?t=1698402706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399860/extras/474063e861fc0994e0d8db59bb8f75e2.mp4?t=1698402706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul> 独特多样的角色技能<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399860/extras/350b9c1d7f3c549513cad6af028e1618.poster.avif?t=1698402706\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it